    question: "What carpet cleaning methods do you use?",
    answer: "We use industry-leading carpet cleaning methods tailored to your home’s needs:\n\n• Steam Cleaning (Hot Water Extraction) – The most powerful method for deep cleaning. It uses hot water and professional equipment to remove embedded dirt, tough stains, dust, and allergens while refreshing carpet fibers.\n• Low-Moisture Cleaning – An effective alternative for certain carpet types or situations where faster drying times are needed.\n\nBoth methods are safe, highly effective, and designed to extend the life and appearance of your carpets while creating a healthier home environment."
