  {
    question: "How often should I have my carpets professionally cleaned?",
    answer: "Most homes benefit from professional carpet cleaning at least once a year to maintain freshness, extend the life of the carpet, and improve indoor air quality.\n\nFor households with children, pets, allergies, or heavy foot traffic, we recommend cleaning every 6 months to keep carpets looking their best and to remove deep-down dirt, dander, and allergens.\n\nDuring your free consultation, we’ll recommend a cleaning schedule that fits your home’s lifestyle and needs."
